content:
A healthy meal that can be made with 5 ingredients or less might be:

* Grilled chicken breast
* Roasted sweet potatoes
* Steamed broccoli
* Olive oil
* Salt and pepper

This meal contains lean protein from the chicken, complex carbohydrates from the sweet potatoes, and essential vitamins and minerals from the broccoli. The olive oil can be used as a healthy fat to dress the vegetables, and salt and pepper can be used to add flavor.
